  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK72">
<l>aṉpilā rellān tamakkuriya raṉpuṭaiyā</l>
<l>reṉpu muriyar piṟarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They who lack love keep everything for themselves; they who have love</l>
<l>keep their very bones for others.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
